  <p>For this moment, our API provide only one endpoint.</p>

  <h3>Creating new conversation</h3>
  <p>HTTP GET Endpoint</p>
  <pre>https://linkchatter.com/get-link</pre>

  <p>Example response</p>
  <pre>
{
  "conversation_id": "mde0odk2nzm2mtm5ndixmjcwmde:d83b2f1422c14016176c75d9c359531f0d7a03b43a560cc2497b55c"
}</pre>

  <p>Link to conversation can be build by following formula</p>
  <pre>https://linkchatter.com/chat/{conversation_id}</pre>
  <p>So that the URL will look like this</p>
  <pre>https://linkchatter.com/chat/mde0odk2nzm2mtm5ndixmjcwmde:d83b2f1422c14016176c75d9c359531f0d7a03b43a560cc2497b55c</pre>
